@base_url = http://localhost:8080
@jwt_token = <your_token_here>
@order_id = 1
@delivery_id = 1

### Get Delivery by Order
GET {{base_url}}/api/deliveries/order/{{order_id}}
Authorization: Bearer {{jwt_token}}

### Update Delivery Status
PATCH {{base_url}}/api/deliveries/{{delivery_id}}/status?status=PICKED_UP
Authorization: Bearer {{jwt_token}}
